                    VLBenchmakrs Version 1.0-beta
                              Karel Lenc
                            Varun Gulshan
                            Andrea Vedaldi


This package implements a collection of benchmkar routines to evaluate
local feature detectors and descriptors. See
http://www.vlfeat.org/benchmarks/index.html for installation and usage
instructions.

The following benchmakrs are implemented:

  A. Wide-baseline matching
    A1. Detector repeatability [1]
    A2. Descriptor matching score [1]
  B. Image retrieval
    B1. Bag-of-words object instance retrieval [2]


DEMO

For the repeatability benchmark demo see file:
  repeatabilityDemo.m
Demo code of the image retrieval benchmark is in file:
  retrievalDemo.m

CHANGES

v1.0-beta  First public release.

